project_address: PLOT NO. 2 SUKRUT RESIDENCY FP 29/2, TP SCHEME -1 JAMNAGAR (VIBHAPAR)
promoterAddress: 401 CITY POINT OPP TOWN HALL Jamnagar 361001

formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
(1) The firm has undertaken development of a Residential Complex under the name of SHLOK HEIGHTS. The firm has procured the Land and the development work is under way, hence the actual Land Cost, Stamp Duty, Registration Fees is considered in respect of the amount to be provided for Estimate in Column A - 1(i)(a) and 1(i)(d).
(2) The firm has obtained Certificate for Estimated Cost of Construction from Mr. HITESH P. PATEL, a Civil Engineer on 22.12.2021.  The amount of Cost of Construction Certified by Engineer in Column A of 1(ii)(ai) is based on the said Certificate net of Land Cost incurred by the firm.
(3) The project is having total 38 Flats at First to Seventh Floors as well 13 shops situated at Ground Floor. The firm has sold 19 Units at SHLOK Heights up to the date of certificate.
(4) This certificate is being issued for RERA compliance for the Shlok Heights Project of M/s. Sagar Enterprise and is based on the records and documents produced before us and explanations provided to us by the Partners of the Firm.
(5) It is not possible for us to verify whether progress of the project as certified by the Architect and Engineer as per Form No. 1 and 2 respectively is in coherence with the actual expenditure incurred and paid.
